  "title": {
    "type": "text",
    "$t": "Mengisi Waktu Libur dengan Beragam Kegiatan, Laporan Kegiatan Komunitas Anak Belajar pada Juli 2024"
  },
  "content": {
    "type": "html",
    "$t": "<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"background: white; margin: 0cm; text-align: justify;\"><span face=\"Verdana, sans-serif\" lang=\"FI\" style=\"font-size: 12pt;\">Salam jumpa teman-teman,<o:p></o:p></span></p>\n\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 6.0pt; margin-left: 0cm; margin-right: 0cm; margin-top: 0cm; margin: 0cm 0cm 6pt;\"><b><span face=\"&quot;Verdana&quot;,sans-serif\" lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size: 16pt; mso-ansi-language: IN; mso-fareast-font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;</span></b></p>\n\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 6.0pt; margin-left: 0cm; margin-right: 0cm; margin-top: 0cm; margin: 0cm 0cm 6pt; text-align: justify;\"><span face=\"&quot;Verdana&quot;,sans-serif\" lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size: 12pt; mso-ansi-language: IN; mso-bidi-font-weight: bold; mso-fareast-font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">Syukur dan t</span><span face=\"&quot;Verdana&quot;,sans-serif\" lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 12pt; mso-bidi-font-weight: bold; mso-fareast-font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">erimakasih </span><span face=\"&quot;Verdana&quot;,sans-serif\" lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size: 12pt; mso-ansi-language: IN; mso-bidi-font-weight: bold; mso-fareast-font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">kami </span><span face=\"&quot;Verdana&quot;,sans-serif\" lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 12pt; mso-bidi-font-weight: bold; mso-fareast-font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">atas </span><span face=\"&quot;Verdana&quot;,sans-serif\" lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size: 12pt; mso-ansi-language: IN; mso-bidi-font-weight: bold; mso-fareast-font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">perhatian, dukungan,\n</span><span face=\"&quot;Verdana&quot;,sans-serif\" lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 12pt; mso-bidi-font-weight: bold; mso-fareast-font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">doa</span><span face=\"&quot;Verdana&quot;,sans-serif\" lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size: 12pt; mso-ansi-language: IN; mso-bidi-font-weight: bold; mso-fareast-font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\"> dan bantuan</span><span face=\"&quot;Verdana&quot;,sans-serif\" lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 12pt; mso-bidi-font-weight: bold; mso-fareast-font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\"> teman-teman </span><span face=\"&quot;Verdana&quot;,sans-serif\" lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size: 12pt; mso-ansi-language: IN; mso-bidi-font-weight: bold; mso-fareast-font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">sehingga\nkegiatan belajar anak-anak Komunitas Anak Belajar tetap bisa berlangsung hingga\nsaat ini.<o:p></o:p></span></p>\n\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 6.0pt; margin-left: 0cm; margin-right: 0cm; margin-top: 0cm; margin: 0cm 0cm 6pt; text-align: justify;\"><span face=\"&quot;Verdana&quot;,sans-serif\" lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size: 12pt; mso-ansi-language: IN; mso-bidi-font-weight: bold; mso-fareast-font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\n\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 6.0pt; margin-left: 0cm; margin-right: 0cm; margin-top: 0cm; margin: 0cm 0cm 6pt; text-align: justify;\"><span face=\"&quot;Verdana&quot;,sans-serif\" lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size: 12pt; mso-ansi-language: EN-GB; mso-bidi-font-weight: bold; mso-fareast-font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">Pada awal Juli 2024,\nanak-anak mengisi libur Panjang sekolah dengan kegiatan luar ruang ke\nAgroedukasi Wisata Ragunan dan Kebun Binatang Ragunan.<o:p></o:p></span></p>\n\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 6.0pt; margin-left: 0cm; margin-right: 0cm; margin-top: 0cm; margin: 0cm 0cm 6pt; text-align: justify;\"><span face=\"&quot;Verdana&quot;,sans-serif\" lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size: 12pt; mso-ansi-language: EN-GB; mso-bidi-font-weight: bold; mso-fareast-font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;</span></p><div class=\"separator\" style=\"clear: both; text-align: center;\"><span face=\"&quot;Verdana&quot;,sans-serif\" lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size: 12pt; mso-ansi-language: EN-GB; mso-bidi-font-weight: bold; mso-fareast-font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\"><a href=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEjoTj4bFczat3Q15PGyhV-tUGC6is7cvk7t-uRp5YIzHiA4Bv0r0k4b4nOB9LwadmllygZs1Cwa-EJHTjc2ah_vYwnsDSQi1I358xnLNbfNKxrv-V6tOOEnqmWWfhII8pohm9zQOH2SFZeD3c-3pL1REPvCT__iMkYZYI_tWUkhY2azZsZrWiCMDKAWmU8Q/s1440/keg.Ragunan0724.2.jpg\" imageanchor=\"1\" style=\"margin-left: 1em; margin-right: 1em;\"><img border=\"0\" data-original-height=\"1440\" data-original-width=\"1440\" height=\"320\" src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEjoTj4bFczat3Q15PGyhV-tUGC6is7cvk7t-uRp5YIzHiA4Bv0r0k4b4nOB9LwadmllygZs1Cwa-EJHTjc2ah_vYwnsDSQi1I358xnLNbfNKxrv-V6tOOEnqmWWfhII8pohm9zQOH2SFZeD3c-3pL1REPvCT__iMkYZYI_tWUkhY2azZsZrWiCMDKAWmU8Q/s320/keg.Ragunan0724.2.jpg\" width=\"320\" /></a></span></div><span face=\"&quot;Verdana&quot;,sans-serif\" lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size: 12pt; mso-ansi-language: EN-GB; mso-bidi-font-weight: bold; mso-fareast-font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\"><br /></span><p></p>\n\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 6.0pt; margin-left: 0cm; margin-right: 0cm; margin-top: 0cm; margin: 0cm 0cm 6pt; text-align: justify;\"><span face=\"&quot;Verdana&quot;,sans-serif\" lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size: 12pt; mso-ansi-language: EN-GB; mso-bidi-font-weight: bold; mso-fareast-font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">Anak-anak bersemangat\nmenimba pengetahuan baru yang langsung mereka lihat dan rasakan di luar tempat\nbelajar anak di Cakung.<o:p></o:p></span></p>\n\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 6.0pt; margin-left: 0cm; margin-right: 0cm; margin-top: 0cm; margin: 0cm 0cm 6pt; text-align: justify;\"><span face=\"&quot;Verdana&quot;,sans-serif\" lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size: 12pt; mso-ansi-language: EN-GB; mso-bidi-font-weight: bold; mso-fareast-font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\n\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 6.0pt; margin-left: 0cm; margin-right: 0cm; margin-top: 0cm; margin: 0cm 0cm 6pt; text-align: justify;\"><span face=\"&quot;Verdana&quot;,sans-serif\" lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size: 12pt; mso-ansi-language: EN-GB; mso-bidi-font-weight: bold; mso-fareast-font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">Terimakasih banyak pada tim\npengajar, Bu Arleta dan keluarga, Pak Heru serta teman-teman Kak Asita yang\nmendampingi anak-anak belajar disana. <o:p></o:p></span></p>\n\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 6.0pt; margin-left: 0cm; margin-right: 0cm; margin-top: 0cm; margin: 0cm 0cm 6pt; text-align: justify;\"><span face=\"&quot;Verdana&quot;,sans-serif\" lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size: 12pt; mso-ansi-language: EN-GB; mso-bidi-font-weight: bold; mso-fareast-font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\n\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 6.0pt; margin-left: 0cm; margin-right: 0cm; margin-top: 0cm; margin: 0cm 0cm 6pt; text-align: justify;\"><span face=\"&quot;Verdana&quot;,sans-serif\" lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size: 12pt; mso-ansi-language: EN-GB; mso-bidi-font-weight: bold; mso-fareast-font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">Pada pertengahan Juli 2024,\nsaat anak-anak sudah mulai masuk sekolah, kami mendapat undangan untuk\nmenghadiri acara pemberian santunan bagi anak yatim dan dhuafa. Ada 15 anak dan\nbeberapa tim pengajar mendampingi anak-anak ke masjid di wilayah Gelora Bung\nKarno. <o:p></o:p></span></p>\n\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 6.0pt; margin-left: 0cm; margin-right: 0cm; margin-top: 0cm; margin: 0cm 0cm 6pt; text-align: justify;\"><span face=\"&quot;Verdana&quot;,sans-serif\" lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size: 12pt; mso-ansi-language: EN-GB; mso-bidi-font-weight: bold; mso-fareast-font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;</span></p><div class=\"separator\" style=\"clear: both; text-align: center;\"><span face=\"&quot;Verdana&quot;,sans-serif\" lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size: 12pt; mso-ansi-language: EN-GB; mso-bidi-font-weight: bold; mso-fareast-font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\"><a href=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEhs90BtD8EIyo4Mgs993lIWQCyyMDUMYC02cgH2KU_gC1BWoLdysM0-hMDT6cKjYDix-fCF4jDSJK0pUiKlIK-7fNhdjpR_ECrSto6gtn4lCQwHrDRckiBCRBEs6j9cMiRPEvi46cGacxz4RSxwB2ICLWAhRMPbk3_M5THREFdMovuHHE58HPYkqQgqL4XT/s2080/AcaraSantunan0724-2.jpg\" imageanchor=\"1\" style=\"margin-left: 1em; margin-right: 1em;\"><img border=\"0\" data-original-height=\"1560\" data-original-width=\"2080\" height=\"240\" src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEhs90BtD8EIyo4Mgs993lIWQCyyMDUMYC02cgH2KU_gC1BWoLdysM0-hMDT6cKjYDix-fCF4jDSJK0pUiKlIK-7fNhdjpR_ECrSto6gtn4lCQwHrDRckiBCRBEs6j9cMiRPEvi46cGacxz4RSxwB2ICLWAhRMPbk3_M5THREFdMovuHHE58HPYkqQgqL4XT/s320/AcaraSantunan0724-2.jpg\" width=\"320\" /></a></span></div><span face=\"&quot;Verdana&quot;,sans-serif\" lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size: 12pt; mso-ansi-language: EN-GB; mso-bidi-font-weight: bold; mso-fareast-font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\"><br /></span><p></p>\n\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 6.0pt; margin-left: 0cm; margin-right: 0cm; margin-top: 0cm; margin: 0cm 0cm 6pt; text-align: justify;\"><span face=\"&quot;Verdana&quot;,sans-serif\" lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size: 12pt; mso-ansi-language: EN-GB; mso-bidi-font-weight: bold; mso-fareast-font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">Kami berterimakasih pada Kak\nQoriah dan panitia penyelenggara acara atas bantuannya pada anak-anak Cakung.<o:p></o:p></span></p>\n\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 6.0pt; margin-left: 0cm; margin-right: 0cm; margin-top: 0cm; margin: 0cm 0cm 6pt; text-align: justify;\"><span face=\"&quot;Verdana&quot;,sans-serif\" lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size: 12pt; mso-ansi-language: EN-GB; mso-bidi-font-weight: bold; mso-fareast-font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\n\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 6.0pt; margin-left: 0cm; margin-right: 0cm; margin-top: 0cm; margin: 0cm 0cm 6pt; text-align: justify;\"><span face=\"&quot;Verdana&quot;,sans-serif\" lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size: 12pt; mso-ansi-language: EN-GB; mso-bidi-font-weight: bold; mso-fareast-font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">Walaupun libur Panjang,\nanak-anak tetap terus mengikuti kegiatan belajar di rumah belajar Cakung.\nJumlah anak belajar pun bertambah hingga 28 peserta aktif. <o:p></o:p></span></p>\n\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 6.0pt; margin-left: 0cm; margin-right: 0cm; margin-top: 0cm; margin: 0cm 0cm 6pt; text-align: justify;\"><span face=\"&quot;Verdana&quot;,sans-serif\" lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size: 12pt; mso-ansi-language: EN-GB; mso-bidi-font-weight: bold; mso-fareast-font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\n\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 6.0pt; margin-left: 0cm; margin-right: 0cm; margin-top: 0cm; margin: 0cm 0cm 6pt; text-align: justify;\"><span face=\"&quot;Verdana&quot;,sans-serif\" lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size: 12pt; mso-ansi-language: EN-GB; mso-bidi-font-weight: bold; mso-fareast-font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">Kami berterimakasih pada tim\npengajar Cakung dan Ciawi, pengurus rumah belajar Cakung dan saung belajar\nCiawi serta para Ibu Cakung dan Ciawi.<o:p></o:p></span></p>\n\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 6.0pt; margin-left: 0cm; margin-right: 0cm; margin-top: 0cm; margin: 0cm 0cm 6pt; text-align: justify;\"><span face=\"&quot;Verdana&quot;,sans-serif\" lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size: 12pt; mso-ansi-language: EN-GB; mso-bidi-font-weight: bold; mso-fareast-font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\n\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 6.0pt; margin-left: 0cm; margin-right: 0cm; margin-top: 0cm; margin: 0cm 0cm 6pt; text-align: justify;\"><span face=\"&quot;Verdana&quot;,sans-serif\" lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size: 12pt; mso-ansi-language: EN-GB; mso-bidi-font-weight: bold; mso-fareast-font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">Terimakasih banyak atas\nkerjasama dan kesetiaannya membantu kegiatan belajar anak.<o:p></o:p></span></p>\n\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 6.0pt; margin-left: 0cm; margin-right: 0cm; margin-top: 0cm; margin: 0cm 0cm 6pt; text-align: justify;\"><span face=\"&quot;Verdana&quot;,sans-serif\" lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size: 12pt; mso-ansi-language: EN-GB; mso-bidi-font-weight: bold; mso-fareast-font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\n\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 6.0pt; margin-left: 0cm; margin-right: 0cm; margin-top: 0cm; margin: 0cm 0cm 6pt; text-align: justify;\"><span face=\"&quot;Verdana&quot;,sans-serif\" lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size: 12pt; mso-ansi-language: EN-GB; mso-bidi-font-weight: bold; mso-fareast-font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">Berikut foto-foto kegiatan\nbelajar, kegiatan luar ruang,</span><span face=\"&quot;Verdana&quot;,sans-serif\" lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"background: white; color: #222222; font-size: 12pt;\"> </span><span face=\"&quot;Verdana&quot;,sans-serif\" lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"background: white; color: #222222; font-size: 12pt;\">dan </span><span face=\"&quot;Verdana&quot;,sans-serif\" lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size: 12pt; mso-ansi-language: EN-GB; mso-bidi-font-weight: bold; mso-fareast-font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">pembagian menu sehat di\nCakung dan Ciawi sepanjang bulan Juli 2024, serta acara pemberian santunan anak\nyatim dan dhuafa.<o:p></o:p></span></p>\n\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 6.0pt; margin-left: 0cm; margin-right: 0cm; margin-top: 0cm; margin: 0cm 0cm 6pt; text-align: justify;\"><span face=\"&quot;Verdana&quot;,sans-serif\" lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size: 12pt; mso-ansi-language: EN-GB; mso-bidi-font-weight: bold; mso-fareast-font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;</span></p><div class=\"separator\" style=\"clear: both; text-align: center;\"><span face=\"&quot;Verdana&quot;,sans-serif\" lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size: 12pt; mso-ansi-language: EN-GB; mso-bidi-font-weight: bold; mso-fareast-font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\"><a href=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEhv8AkYHriC97aBHBCJZCzHFnhQZlxhqcAayEmFQRlAu9HSGDCcpOYFOsP7tnLcvanP6gDCWgeK1zbFsqVAk81NfBeFwYGony2r_oxUbB118__HcbbNAvhhVqzrRGzq1ietKIQUOlTdjRA-AemGr6DOLGi02ihpntQwXThsDLEw1wtQA_iPx-PoHrPJWj9i/s1440/keg.belajar0724.2.jpg\" imageanchor=\"1\" style=\"margin-left: 1em; margin-right: 1em;\"><img border=\"0\" data-original-height=\"1440\" data-original-width=\"1440\" height=\"320\" src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEhv8AkYHriC97aBHBCJZCzHFnhQZlxhqcAayEmFQRlAu9HSGDCcpOYFOsP7tnLcvanP6gDCWgeK1zbFsqVAk81NfBeFwYGony2r_oxUbB118__HcbbNAvhhVqzrRGzq1ietKIQUOlTdjRA-AemGr6DOLGi02ihpntQwXThsDLEw1wtQA_iPx-PoHrPJWj9i/s320/keg.belajar0724.2.jpg\" width=\"320\" /></a></span></div><div class=\"separator\" style=\"clear: both; text-align: center;\"><span face=\"&quot;Verdana&quot;,sans-serif\" lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size: 12pt; mso-ansi-language: EN-GB; mso-bidi-font-weight: bold; mso-fareast-font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\"><a href=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEgXwJpZsA1bgH9whyphenhyphenClaXmnr7YfmKwlEeM8nl-ffLYhCispSO3W46dC1V0WoRBksHM5Ya1jfl0FvLG2BQDVwO3POEqzXUSEy-tA6VvVzYUVd_H1hjSeIcZ9SjCFsTauPcHq5C4lWnlEycy0MRbewq1_Mq92mwHBb_ac_VTD1iHpveK9iqlBtxnoZJfqp0P3/s1440/Menusehat0724.2.jpg\" imageanchor=\"1\" style=\"margin-left: 1em; margin-right: 1em;\"><img border=\"0\" data-original-height=\"1440\" data-original-width=\"1440\" height=\"320\" src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEgXwJpZsA1bgH9whyphenhyphenClaXmnr7YfmKwlEeM8nl-ffLYhCispSO3W46dC1V0WoRBksHM5Ya1jfl0FvLG2BQDVwO3POEqzXUSEy-tA6VvVzYUVd_H1hjSeIcZ9SjCFsTauPcHq5C4lWnlEycy0MRbewq1_Mq92mwHBb_ac_VTD1iHpveK9iqlBtxnoZJfqp0P3/s320/Menusehat0724.2.jpg\" width=\"320\" /></a></span></div><span face=\"&quot;Verdana&quot;,sans-serif\" lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size: 12pt; mso-ansi-language: EN-GB; mso-bidi-font-weight: bold; mso-fareast-font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\"><br /><div class=\"separator\" style=\"clear: both; text-align: center;\"><br /></div></span><p></p>\n\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 6.0pt; margin-left: 0cm; margin-right: 0cm; margin-top: 0cm; margin: 0cm 0cm 6pt; text-align: justify;\"><span face=\"&quot;Verdana&quot;,sans-serif\" lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size: 12pt; mso-ansi-language: EN-GB; mso-bidi-font-weight: bold; mso-fareast-font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">Kami berterimakasih pada\nteman-teman yang setia membantu berjalannya kegiatan Komunitas Anak Belajar,\nbaik dalam doa, bantuan finansial maupun bantuan material.<o:p></o:p></span></p>\n\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 6.0pt; margin-left: 0cm; margin-right: 0cm; margin-top: 0cm; margin: 0cm 0cm 6pt; text-align: justify;\"><span face=\"&quot;Verdana&quot;,sans-serif\" lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size: 12pt; mso-ansi-language: EN-GB; mso-bidi-font-weight: bold; mso-fareast-font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\n\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 6.0pt; margin-left: 0cm; margin-right: 0cm; margin-top: 0cm; margin: 0cm 0cm 6pt; text-align: justify;\"><span face=\"&quot;Verdana&quot;,sans-serif\" lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size: 12pt; mso-ansi-language: EN-GB; mso-bidi-font-weight: bold; mso-fareast-font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">Terimakasih kami pada Bu Arleta\ndan teman-teman Kak Asita atas bantuan pakaian layak pakai dan paket buku dan\nalat tulis. Kami juga berterimakasih pada Kak Justin atas bantuan buku-buku\npelajaran SD dan SMP layak pakai. <o:p></o:p></span></p>\n\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 6.0pt; margin-left: 0cm; margin-right: 0cm; margin-top: 0cm; margin: 0cm 0cm 6pt; text-align: justify;\"><span face=\"&quot;Verdana&quot;,sans-serif\" lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size: 12pt; mso-ansi-language: EN-GB; mso-bidi-font-weight: bold; mso-fareast-font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\n\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"background: white; margin-bottom: 6.0pt; margin-left: 0cm; margin-right: 0cm; margin-top: 0cm; margin: 0cm 0cm 6pt; text-align: justify;\"><span face=\"Verdana, sans-serif\" lang=\"FI\" style=\"font-size: 12pt;\">Kiranya Tuhan berkenan\nmemberi kesehatan prima dan berkat limpah. Harapan kami, kerjasama yang telah\ndijalin selama ini dapat terus berlanjut dengan baik. <o:p></o:p></span></p>\n\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 6.0pt; margin-left: 0cm; margin-right: 0cm; margin-top: 0cm; margin: 0cm 0cm 6pt; text-align: justify;\"><span face=\"&quot;Verdana&quot;,sans-serif\" lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size: 12pt; mso-ansi-language: EN-GB; mso-bidi-font-weight: bold; mso-fareast-font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\n\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height: 115%; margin-bottom: 10.0pt; margin-left: 0cm; margin-right: 0cm; margin-top: 0cm; margin: 0cm 0cm 10pt; text-align: justify;\"><b><span face=\"&quot;Verdana&quot;,sans-serif\" lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"background: white; color: #222222; font-size: 12pt; line-height: 115%;\">Saat ini dana operasional\nkegiatan bulan Agustus sangat terbatas. Kebutuhan dana operasional kegiatan\nKomunitas Anak Belajar bulan Agustus 2024 terlampir. <o:p></o:p></span></b></p>\n\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height: 115%; margin-bottom: 10.0pt; margin-left: 0cm; margin-right: 0cm; margin-top: 0cm; margin: 0cm 0cm 10pt; text-align: justify;\"><b><span face=\"&quot;Verdana&quot;,sans-serif\" lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size: 12pt; line-height: 115%; mso-ansi-language: IN; mso-fareast-font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; mso-fareast-language: IN;\">Kami mengajak teman-teman semua untuk tetap setia\nberpartisipasi dan mendukung kegiatan </span></b><b><span face=\"&quot;Verdana&quot;,sans-serif\" lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"background: white; color: #222222; font-size: 12pt; line-height: 115%;\">kami dengan harapan bisa\nmemberikan bantuan dana rutin operasional per bulan untuk pemenuhan kebutuhan\nkegiatan Komunitas Anak Belajar 2024.&nbsp; <o:p></o:p></span></b></p>\n\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"background: white; margin: 0cm; text-align: justify;\"><span face=\"Verdana, sans-serif\" lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size: 12pt;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\n\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"background: white; margin-bottom: 6.0pt; margin-left: 0cm; margin-right: 0cm; margin-top: 0cm; margin: 0cm 0cm 6pt; text-align: justify;\"><span face=\"Verdana, sans-serif\" lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size: 12pt;\">Adalah tanggung jawab kita\nbersama untuk ambil bagian dalam karya sosial ini demi mencerdaskan anak-anak\nbangsa dan demi kesejahteraan masyarakat yang kami dampingi khususnya serta\ndemi tegaknya keadilan sosial bagi seluruh masyarakat Indonesia. <o:p></o:p></span></p>\n\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"background: white; margin-bottom: 6.0pt; margin-left: 0cm; margin-right: 0cm; margin-top: 0cm; margin: 0cm 0cm 6pt; text-align: justify;\"><span face=\"Verdana, sans-serif\" lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size: 12pt;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\n\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height: 115%; margin-bottom: 10.0pt; margin-left: 0cm; margin-right: 0cm; margin-top: 0cm; margin: 0cm 0cm 10pt; text-align: justify;\"><span face=\"&quot;Verdana&quot;,sans-serif\" lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size: 12pt; line-height: 115%; mso-ansi-language: IN; mso-fareast-font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; mso-fareast-language: IN;\">Perhatian dan dukungan teman-teman memberi kekuatan bagi kami untuk tetap\nsetia menjalankan karya dan pelayanan ini.<o:p></o:p></span></p>\n\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height: 115%; margin-bottom: 10.0pt; margin-left: 0cm; margin-right: 0cm; margin-top: 0cm; margin: 0cm 0cm 10pt; text-align: justify;\"><span face=\"&quot;Verdana&quot;,sans-serif\" lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size: 12pt; line-height: 115%; mso-ansi-language: EN-GB; mso-bidi-font-weight: bold; mso-fareast-font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\n\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"background: white; margin-bottom: 6.0pt; margin-left: 0cm; margin-right: 0cm; margin-top: 0cm; margin: 0cm 0cm 6pt; text-align: justify;\"><b><span face=\"Verdana, sans-serif\" lang=\"IT\" style=\"font-size: 12pt;\">Rencana kegiatan di bulan </span></b><b><span face=\"Verdana, sans-serif\" lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 12pt;\">Agustus </span></b><b><span face=\"Verdana, sans-serif\" lang=\"IT\" style=\"font-size: 12pt;\">20</span></b><b><span face=\"Verdana, sans-serif\" lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size: 12pt;\">2</span></b><b><span face=\"Verdana, sans-serif\" lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 12pt;\">4</span></b><b><span face=\"Verdana, sans-serif\" lang=\"IT\" style=\"font-size: 12pt;\"> ini adalah :</span></b><b><span face=\"Verdana, sans-serif\" lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size: 12pt;\"><o:p></o:p></span></b></p>\n\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"background: white; margin-bottom: 6.0pt; margin-left: 0cm; margin-right: 0cm; margin-top: 0cm; margin: 0cm 0cm 6pt; text-align: justify;\"><b><span face=\"Verdana, sans-serif\" lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size: 12pt;\">&nbsp;</span></b></p>\n\n<ol start=\"1\" style=\"margin-top: 0cm;\" type=\"1\">\n <li class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"background: white; margin-bottom: 6pt; margin-top: 0cm; text-align: justify;\"><b><span face=\"&quot;Verdana&quot;,sans-serif\" lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 12pt; mso-fareast-font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">Kegiatan\n     Belajar</span></b><b><span face=\"&quot;Verdana&quot;,sans-serif\" lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 12pt; mso-ansi-language: IN; mso-fareast-font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\"> </span></b><b><span face=\"&quot;Verdana&quot;,sans-serif\" lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 12pt; mso-fareast-font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\"><o:p></o:p></span></b></li>\n <ol start=\"1\" style=\"margin-top: 0cm;\" type=\"a\">\n  <li class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"background: white; margin-bottom: 6pt; margin-top: 0cm; text-align: justify;\"><span face=\"&quot;Verdana&quot;,sans-serif\" lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 12pt; mso-bidi-font-weight: bold; mso-fareast-font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">Kegiatan\n      belajar setiap hari Senin dan Kamis di Cakung dan setiap Jumat di Ciawi.</span><span face=\"&quot;Verdana&quot;,sans-serif\" lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size: 12pt; mso-ansi-language: EN-GB; mso-fareast-font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\"><o:p></o:p></span></li>\n  <li class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"background: white; margin-bottom: 6pt; margin-top: 0cm; text-align: justify;\"><span face=\"&quot;Verdana&quot;,sans-serif\" lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 12pt; mso-bidi-font-weight: bold; mso-fareast-font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">Evaluasi\n      belajar anak caturwulan II yang akan diselenggarakan pada minggu terakhir\n      Agustus 2024.</span><span face=\"&quot;Verdana&quot;,sans-serif\" lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size: 12pt; mso-ansi-language: EN-GB; mso-fareast-font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\"><o:p></o:p></span></li>\n </ol>\n</ol>\n\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"background: white; margin-bottom: 6.0pt; margin-left: 72.0pt; margin-right: 0cm; margin-top: 0cm; margin: 0cm 0cm 6pt 72pt; text-align: justify;\"><span face=\"Verdana, sans-serif\" lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size: 12pt;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\n\n<ol start=\"2\" style=\"margin-top: 0cm;\" type=\"1\">\n <li class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"background: white; margin-bottom: 6pt; margin-top: 0cm; text-align: justify;\"><b><span face=\"&quot;Verdana&quot;,sans-serif\" lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size: 12pt; mso-ansi-language: EN-GB; mso-fareast-font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">Kegiatan\n     Wirausaha Remaja dan Ibu<o:p></o:p></span></b></li>\n <ol start=\"1\" style=\"margin-top: 0cm;\" type=\"a\">\n  <li class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"background: white; margin-bottom: 6pt; margin-top: 0cm; text-align: justify;\"><span face=\"&quot;Verdana&quot;,sans-serif\" lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size: 12pt; mso-ansi-language: EN-GB; mso-fareast-font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">Pertemuan\n      kerjasama dengan tenaga pelatih menjahit untuk rencana dibuka kegiatan\n      pelatihan menjahit di rumah belajar Cakung.&nbsp; <o:p></o:p></span></li>\n </ol>\n</ol>\n\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"background: white; margin-bottom: 6.0pt; margin-left: 0cm; margin-right: 0cm; margin-top: 0cm; margin: 0cm 0cm 6pt; text-align: justify;\"><span face=\"Verdana, sans-serif\" lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size: 12pt;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\n\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"background: white; margin-bottom: 6.0pt; margin-left: 0cm; margin-right: 0cm; margin-top: 0cm; margin: 0cm 0cm 6pt; text-align: justify;\"><span face=\"Verdana, sans-serif\" lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size: 12pt;\">Akhirnya k</span><span face=\"Verdana, sans-serif\" lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 12pt;\">ami ucapkan banyak terimakasih pada teman-teman\nyang telah banyak mendukung dalam doa dan dana, tenaga, maupun material untuk\nterwujudnya program kegiatan Komunitas Anak Belajar sepanjang bulan ini. </span><span face=\"Verdana, sans-serif\" lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size: 12pt;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\n\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"background: white; margin-bottom: 6.0pt; margin-left: 0cm; margin-right: 0cm; margin-top: 0cm; margin: 0cm 0cm 6pt; text-align: justify;\"><span face=\"Verdana, sans-serif\" lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size: 12pt;\">&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></span></p>\n\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height: 115%; margin-bottom: 10.0pt; margin-left: 0cm; margin-right: 0cm; margin-top: 0cm; margin: 0cm 0cm 10pt; text-align: justify;\"><span face=\"Verdana, sans-serif\" lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 12pt; line-height: 115%;\">Terimakasih kami pada para donatur atas bantuan dana </span><span face=\"Verdana, sans-serif\" lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size: 12pt; line-height: 115%;\">rutin </span><span face=\"Verdana, sans-serif\" lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 12pt; line-height: 115%;\">yang amat sangat mendukung\nterselenggaranya operasional program Komunitas Anak Belajar. </span><span face=\"&quot;Verdana&quot;,sans-serif\" lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size: 12pt; line-height: 115%; mso-ansi-language: IN; mso-fareast-font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; mso-fareast-language: IN;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\n\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"background: white; margin-bottom: 6.0pt; margin-left: 0cm; margin-right: 0cm; margin-top: 0cm; margin: 0cm 0cm 6pt; text-align: justify;\"><span face=\"Verdana, sans-serif\" lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 12pt;\">Terimakasih banyak atas bantuan yang </span><span face=\"Verdana, sans-serif\" lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size: 12pt;\">sangat berguna demi\nkelangsungan kegiatan belajar anak-anak dan kemajuan generasi penerus bangsa. <o:p></o:p></span></p>\n\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"background: white; margin-bottom: 6.0pt; margin-left: 0cm; margin-right: 0cm; margin-top: 0cm; margin: 0cm 0cm 6pt; text-align: justify;\"><span face=\"Verdana, sans-serif\" lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size: 12pt;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\n\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"background: white; margin-bottom: 6.0pt; margin-left: 0cm; margin-right: 0cm; margin-top: 0cm; margin: 0cm 0cm 6pt; text-align: justify;\"><span face=\"Verdana, sans-serif\" lang=\"FI\" style=\"font-size: 12pt;\">Terimakasih banyak atas </span><span face=\"Verdana, sans-serif\" lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size: 12pt;\">kesetiaan, kepercayaan, dan\n</span><span face=\"Verdana, sans-serif\" lang=\"FI\" style=\"font-size: 12pt;\">semua\nkebaikannya. <o:p></o:p></span></p>\n\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"background: white; margin-bottom: 6.0pt; margin-left: 0cm; margin-right: 0cm; margin-top: 0cm; margin: 0cm 0cm 6pt; text-align: justify;\"><span face=\"Verdana, sans-serif\" lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size: 12pt;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\n\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"background: white; margin-bottom: 6.0pt; margin-left: 0cm; margin-right: 0cm; margin-top: 0cm; margin: 0cm 0cm 6pt; text-align: justify;\"><a name=\"_Hlk171546814\"><span face=\"Verdana, sans-serif\" lang=\"FI\" style=\"font-size: 12pt;\">Kiranya Tuhan berkenan\nmemberi kesehatan prima dan berkat limpah, dan harapan kami, kerjasama yang\ntelah dijalin selama ini dapat terus berlanjut dengan baik. </span></a><span face=\"Verdana, sans-serif\" lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size: 12pt;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"background: white; margin-bottom: 6.0pt; margin-left: 0cm; margin-right: 0cm; margin-top: 0cm; margin: 0cm 0cm 6pt; text-align: justify;\"><span face=\"Verdana, sans-serif\" lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size: 12pt;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\n\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"background: white; margin-bottom: 6.0pt; margin-left: 0cm; margin-right: 0cm; margin-top: 0cm; margin: 0cm 0cm 6pt; text-align: justify;\"><span face=\"Verdana, sans-serif\" lang=\"FI\" style=\"font-size: 12pt;\">Kita diutus untuk membawa\ndamai sejahtera di dunia ini. </span><span face=\"Verdana, sans-serif\" lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size: 12pt;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\n\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"background: white; margin-bottom: 6.0pt; margin-left: 0cm; margin-right: 0cm; margin-top: 0cm; margin: 0cm 0cm 6pt; text-align: justify;\"><span face=\"Verdana, sans-serif\" lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size: 12pt;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\n\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"background: white; margin-bottom: 6.0pt; margin-left: 0cm; margin-right: 0cm; margin-top: 0cm; margin: 0cm 0cm 6pt; text-align: justify;\"><span face=\"Verdana, sans-serif\" lang=\"FI\" style=\"font-size: 12pt;\">Tuhan memberkati kita\nsemua.<o:p></o:p></span></p>\n\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"background: white; margin-bottom: 6.0pt; margin-left: 0cm; margin-right: 0cm; margin-top: 0cm; margin: 0cm 0cm 6pt; text-align: justify;\"><span face=\"Verdana, sans-serif\" lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 12pt;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\n\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"background: white; margin-bottom: 6.0pt; margin-left: 0cm; margin-right: 0cm; margin-top: 0cm; margin: 0cm 0cm 6pt; text-align: justify;\"><span face=\"Verdana, sans-serif\" lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 12pt;\">Laporan kegiatan bulanan dapat diakses dalam\nblog kami di : <b><a href=\"http://cakungchildrencommunity.blogspot.com/\">http://cakungchildrencommunity.blogspot.com</a>.<o:p></o:p></b></span></p>\n\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"background: white; margin-bottom: 6.0pt; margin-left: 0cm; margin-right: 0cm; margin-top: 0cm; margin: 0cm 0cm 6pt; text-align: justify;\"><span face=\"Verdana, sans-serif\" lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 12pt;\">Produksi ketrampilan warga dapat dipesan dan\ndiakses dalam blog kami di : <b><a href=\"http://cakungchildrencreation.blogspot.com/\">http://cakungchildrencreation.blogspot.com</a>.<o:p></o:p></b></span></p>\n\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"background: white; margin-bottom: 6.0pt; margin-left: 0cm; margin-right: 0cm; margin-top: 0cm; margin: 0cm 0cm 6pt; text-align: justify;\"><span face=\"Verdana, sans-serif\" lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size: 12pt;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\n\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"background: white; margin-bottom: 6.0pt; margin-left: 0cm; margin-right: 0cm; margin-top: 0cm; margin: 0cm 0cm 6pt; text-align: justify;\"><span face=\"Verdana, sans-serif\" lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size: 12pt;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\n\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"background: white; margin-bottom: 6.0pt; margin-left: 0cm; margin-right: 0cm; margin-top: 0cm; margin: 0cm 0cm 6pt; text-align: justify;\"><span face=\"Verdana, sans-serif\" lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 12pt;\">&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></span></p>\n\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"background: white; margin-bottom: 6.0pt; margin-left: 0cm; margin-right: 0cm; margin-top: 0cm; margin: 0cm 0cm 6pt; text-align: justify;\"><span face=\"Verdana, sans-serif\" 